<hr>
<Title Size="Size.Size4" IsSpaced>
    左右滚动Table
</Title>
<Content>
    您可以通过添加WithContainer属性将表格包装在table-container元素中来创建可滚动表格
</Content>

<Table WithContainer IsBordered>
    @for (int i = 0; i < 5; i++)
    {
        <tr>
            @for (int j = 1; j <= 50; j++)
            {
                <td>@(i.ToString()+"."+j.ToString())</td>
            }
        </tr>
    }

</Table>